social_posts.post_text: June⚡️9⚡️2023 Weatherford Texas
Great people, Great horses, Great Ranch, Greatness! 📷

Just a day in the life if @slusherphoto ⚡️ all in the same day Busy Texas streets to Lonely west Texas. I ask myself everyday which do I like better. And I always answer Both for right now. Grateful to have the opportunity to experience both.  And to have good quality 100%er friends to hangout with. #slusherphoto #texas
You only turn 13 once!  We are doing things right. @lisaslusher @cusscowboy @slushernancy

Where did it come from. Images find me and I find them. I know it when I click the button but sometimes I don’t see it until on the computer screen. We need more bronc rides. This is one is LIMITED. 2/25!
It was a Good Day. It’s always a good day. Just need to slow down a little slow my mind down. I’m definitely the Hippie. Thanks @gerrygesell & @tylercrowart
Still the best thing since sliced bread. @americanhatco @besthatstore @jppelham
Texas Brags” with @emilyvvinson  Styling ⚡️ @stefannypac  HMU ⚡️ @jackietzang  Agency ⚡️ @wallflowermgmt
Top 10 weekend with Lisa and State and some of our good friends at the M3 Gather Ranch Rodeo. So many highlights. Swimming after a Ranch Rodeo is always a good idea.
How about @luckybdesign putting on the show @besthatstore nothing like Hand painted Advertising like it was done 50 years ago.

I’m sitting here listening to a great podcast with @wilsoncapron @cary.schwarz @mwcapron  and it’s really inspiring to listen to all 3 of them talk about art and inspiration and roping and cowboying. I have learned to appreciate the people I’m around bc I know they enjoy being around me and I surround myself with people who are true friends. Not just in this post who I have tagged you know who you are. @mwcapron has a lot figured out but he always willing to learn more and open to new ideas. Positive thinking has positive outcomes.
Summer Time!
This limited edition 60x40 image “CowCamp Breaking” is being sold ON LINE  in New Western Talent show. Along with 2 other of mine. @westerngallery ➕✖️

How it happened.. The first I went to the 6’s. Too many stories to put on here. But one of the best places I’ve been. All my friends were there and made it extra fun. The TeePee shot almost didn’t happen. I was walking from my teepee to the fly to eat dinner and left my camera in the teepee why? Well it’s the last time I’ve not had it with me so I learned a valuable lesson. I looked over and thought wow what a perfect setting and well the rest is now printed and one of my favorites. It’s called “Spring Works 6’s” a limited edition 40x30 ONLINE SALE @westerngallery
Photo Drop form a trip to Colorado with State and @chad_rohde and his boys. More to come.
How it all comes together. Only the first one is For Sale on @westerngallery ONLINE SALE. @gerrygesell always making it easy and fun.
Dang good week! Dang good week. Grateful for these weeks and people I get to be around. I got to work on my skills this week. Thank you @tsquared.terry and @x_cross_x_ranch_

How to get the perfect portrait of someone who is working and trying to do something important. I’m always trying to find the perfect situation. It’s all about timing.
Definitely mornings Vibes. Framed on a wall would be a great way to start your day.

It’s all about the AllSup’s!  Especially with a wiener dog.  Spur Texas!!

Cowboys Like us! This is @x_cross_x_ranch_ son but in all honesty I wish it was a picture of me when I was little. If we all look back this is what we imagined. At least I did. And a few times it happened when I was little but i was never cut loose. Now maybe that was my grandpa or maybe it was the horse I was put on. Life is short and good horses are what it’s all about.  I guess what I’m saying is dream and let loose and have fun. Anyone who’s not letting that happen just ride right on past. #greenlight
